interaction.name: Jon Snow
interaction.content: If I fall, don't bring me back.

interaction.name: Sansa Stark
interaction.content: I hate the king more than any of them.

interaction.name: Eddard "Ned" Stark
interaction.content: The man who passes the sentence should swing the sword.

interaction.name: Jaime Lannister
interaction.content: The things I do for love.

interaction.name: Tyrion Lannister
interaction.content: I have a tender spot in my heart for cripples, bastards and broken things.

interaction.name: Sansa Stark
interaction.content: No need to seize the last word, Lord Baelish. I'll assume it was something clever.

interaction.name: Tywin Lannister
interaction.content: A lion does not concern himself with the opinion of sheep.

interaction.name: Cersei Lannister
interaction.content: When you play the game of thrones, you win or you die. There is no middle ground.

interaction.name: Ramsay Bolton
interaction.content: If you think this has a happy ending, you haven't been paying attention.

interaction.name: Mance Rayder
interaction.content: The freedom to make my own mistakes was all I ever wanted.

interaction.name: Olenna Tyrell
interaction.content: The world is overflowing with horrible things, but theyâ€™re all a tray of cakes next to death.
